00:33:43.750 --> 00:33:47.650
and no one seemed bored at all.

00:33:47.650 --> 00:33:51.400
I don't know, is this
just a general malaise?

00:33:51.400 --> 00:33:51.900
OK.

00:33:51.900 --> 00:33:53.770
Because I would have thought,
if you've got more things to do,

00:33:53.770 --> 00:33:55.700
it's just a question
of having-- there

00:33:55.700 --> 00:33:57.660
are challenges with attention.

00:33:57.660 --> 00:33:58.889
Absolutely no doubt about it.

00:33:58.889 --> 00:34:00.930
There are challenges with
sticking with something

00:34:00.930 --> 00:34:03.300
long enough to enjoy it.

00:34:03.300 --> 00:34:05.790
But I don't know if I can
answer that better than that.

00:34:05.790 --> 00:34:08.639
AUDIENCE: It's probably related
to lack of attention span.

00:34:08.639 --> 00:34:10.820
Over time, we've
